{"type":"message","id":"fdf537c2","parentId":"2dbfa506","timestamp":"2026-03-20T16:07:28.965Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-21 00:07 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下行业的最新动态：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n要求：\n1. 搜索最新（2026年3月）的行业动态、政策、市场趋势\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 每条信息包含：标题、来源、摘要、日期\n4. 输出格式：Markdown 列表\n\n请直接输出搜索结果，不要添加其他内容。"}],"timestamp":1774022848964}}
{"type":"message","id":"99f49bd9","parentId":"fdf537c2","timestamp":"2026-03-20T16:07:33.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我搜索4个行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务。需要整理3-5条关键信息，每条包含标题、来源、摘要、日期，输出为Markdown列表。\n\n我需要使用web-search skill来搜索这些信息。让我先读取这个skill的文件。","thinkingSignature":"f370b18271433501459c59c9458b6e663f36169e46bb66568a392a89d6fc3930"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a5ge2xdpd898_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":108,"output":109,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30649,"totalTokens":30866,"cost":{"input":0.0000324,"output":0.00013079999999999998,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0036778799999999997,"total":0.0038410799999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774022848965}}
{"type":"message","id":"0fe54213","parentId":"99f49bd9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T16:07:33.527Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a5ge2xdpd898_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774022853525}}
{"type":"message","id":"207146d6","parentId":"0fe54213","timestamp":"2026-03-20T16:07:37.330Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我知道如何使用web搜索了。我需要搜索4个行业的最新动态。让我分别为每个行业进行搜索，然后整理结果。\n\n我需要搜索：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026年3月\n2. 智能安防 2026年3月\n3. 网络系统集成 2026年3月\n4. IT运维服务 2026年3月\n\n让我分别搜索这4个行业。","thinkingSignature":"d97f7855ae2a977195184f3021706920a0495e4f6c978ca48664a2cb5689a0db"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9sdqm7kfeol3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 行业动态 政策\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":890,"output":144,"cacheRead":30491,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31525,"cost":{"input":0.000267,"output":0.0001728,"cacheRead":0.0009147299999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013545299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774022853527}}
